pento.store
Interface PentoStore

All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultPentoStore
public interface PentoStore

Defines the storage and query interface for Pento instances. The behavior of the store, specifically the terms by which read PentoCallback and write PentoCallback are informed of storage operations are implementation specific.
